1
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:26,800
Xinyue,

2
00:00:27,719 --> 00:00:28,640
thanks to your

3
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:30,359
calmness in danger,

4
00:00:30,359 --> 00:00:31,559
we were able to fight the epidemic.

5
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:42,119
Thanks to Sister Su,

6
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:44,159
