7
00:00:44,679 --> 00:00:45,640
to borrow the medicine.

8
00:00:52,159 --> 00:00:52,960
Thanks to Yan Ge,

9
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,240
who risked her life

10
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:56,439
to search for the source of the epidemic,

11
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:59,840
we were able to develop a prescription.

12
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:13,000
Thank you, Sir,

13
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,159
