14
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,319
and accompanying me

15
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:17,840
to diagnose and treat patients.

16
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:35,319
Thank you, Nong.

17
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,280
You're doing well.

18
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:47,920
Of course,

19
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:49,599
I also want to thank Yunzhou

20
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:52,599
for working with major medicine merchants

21
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:54,359
to let the people know

22
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,120
the harm of keeping corpses

23
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,719
at home during an epidemic.

24
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:13,599
Alright.

25
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,240
After this epidemic,

26
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,159
I've realized that when we unite,

27
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,360
we can achieve so much

28
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,680
and protect so many people.

29
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:25,520
It's my honor to practice medicine

30
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:27,199
