33
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,400
To life.

34
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:39,759
To sincerity.

35
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,080
To freedom.

36
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,719
To the people.

37
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:45,360
To hope.

38
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:46,520
To...

39
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,599
To all of you.

40
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:15,960
People

41
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:21,199
