42
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:25,240
yet they don't allow women's skirts

43
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:27,599
to flutter in the wind.

44
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,159
But

45
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:33,199
now we can finally

46
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:38,479
stand tall and face the wind,

47
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:40,919
neither humble

48
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:42,719
nor arrogant.

49
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:43,960
That's right.

50
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:47,400
Maintaining a sense of warmth

51
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,840
is a remarkable thing.

52
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:51,719
Exactly.

53
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,000
You

54
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:58,919
have lit the way for countless people walking in the dark,

55
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:02,719
including me.

56
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,639
Then let's continue to do

57
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:12,800
