63
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:40,120
Do you love me?

64
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:41,000
I do.

65
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,000
And you?

66
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:49,040
I do.

67
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,839
Shi'an,

68
