69
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,000
I want...

70
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,959
I want to be with you.

71
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,839
Yan Ge,

72
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:43,879
I...

73
