76
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,399
Congratulations.

77
00:06:12,079 --> 00:06:12,519
Congratulations.

78
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,160
But...

79
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,639
