94
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,560
Is it because I'm not good enough for you?

95
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:36,920
Is it because

96
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,240
I have an

97
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,120
