98
00:07:41,199 --> 00:07:42,279
I'll never be good enough for you.

99
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:42,800
No.

100
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,079
It's not like that.

101
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:46,879
I'm the one who's not good enough for you.

102
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:55,199
But I can't keep you.

103
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,319
I can't keep you.

